# Create a New Microsoft Account

- [] Navigate to @[www.outlook.com][outlook]{powershell}

- [] Select the browser you prefer, check the **Always use this app** box, and click **OK**
- [] On the outlook home page, click **Create Account**

- [] On the create account page, input a new email name and password of your choosing, then click **Next.**

- [] Add your First Name and the Last Name +++AzurePass+++, then click **Next.**

- [] Select your Country/Region and Birthdate, then click **Next.**

- [] Put in a **Valid** cell phone number, and click **Send Code.**

- [] You will receive a text message with a numerical code, input that in the **Enter the access code** field.

- [] Progress through all the prompts until you end up in your new inbox.


[outlook]:
```
Start-Process 'http://www.outlook.com'
```
